data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: A woman is wandering on the street. She wears a pair of tight trousers and high heels. There is a large plastic bag in her hand. She looks down as if thinking of something. She is passing a shop. In front of the shop hung a picture of a man who looked very excited. She might go to the shop to do some shopping. Most women like shopping very much, while most men dislike it on the other hand. For most women, shopping is an excellent way to relax and enjoy themselves when they walk through the malls searching for their favorite clothes and cosmetics. （105 字）
